  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large skillet, heat the olive oil over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the chicken to the skillet and cook until browned, about 5-6 minutes.",
    "Add the onion and garlic to the skillet and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Stir in the smoky paprika, diced tomatoes, and chicken broth.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and let cook for 10-15 minutes.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a 9x13 inch baking dish.",
    "Top the mixture with the shredded cheese and breadcrumbs.",
    "Bake the casserole in the preheated oven for 20-25 minutes, or until the cheese is melted and bubbly.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
